cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as image segmentation and 3D reconstruction, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The proposed method is also applicable to robotics and human-robot interaction, which fall under cs.RO. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) suggests that the paper may also be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves clustering algorithms, which could be categorized under cs.GR (graphics).
